Ollama – to run local language models

LLaMA 3 / Mistral / Phi-2 – open-source LLMs

LangChain – RAG pipeline builder

LlamaIndex – alternative RAG framework

FAISS – vector database for semantic search

SentenceTransformers – for generating embeddings

PyMuPDF – extract text from PDF files

docx2txt – extract text from DOCX files

Python 3.10+ – programming language

FastAPI – backend API framework

Uvicorn – server to run FastAPI

pydantic – data validation (used by FastAPI)

python-multipart – for file upload handling

HTML5 – frontend structure

CSS3 – frontend styling

JavaScript – frontend interactivity

ABB Internal Server / VM – for hosting

Firewall / VPN – for secure internal access
